{"tid":1671305,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Blizzcon] [Gamers for Freedom] 自問係Gamers嘅同我入黎 !!!","createTime":"2019-10-23T11:37:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T11:43:54.000Z","uid":54472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e25c76b3d85b11c3bea0cb74b002ff421c987169","tid":1671305,"uid":54472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:37:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地仲記唔記得blizzard點樣奶共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 11月2號就係Blizzcon 2019  作為Blizzard嘅大日子 我地當然要賀一賀佢啦 但係care freedom of speech 同 game censorship嘅唔係淨係得我地香港人 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">出面有更多嘅人記得我地 connect到我地 想一齊對抗blizzard同支共 我地一定唔可以唔理呢條戰線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有gamers仲好有心整埋網站 <a href=\"https://www.gamersforfreedom.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gamersforfreedom.com&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yG1VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=ccf9b35a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gamersforfreedom.com</a> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n想號召更多人參與佢地去blizzcon嘅示威  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想像下喺blizzcon咁搞 可以reach幾多嘅來自全世界嘅人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n可以sign petition, 推佢地fb event, share佢地嘅文宣, cosplay去blizzcon示威, join佢地discord, 教你delete blizzard ac, 仲推介埋唔玩blizzard game嘅新選擇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係佢地絕對未夠人 我地就算去唔到現場 都有要去幫手宣傳下佢地嘅行動 fb又好tw又好 希望將呢樣野spread開去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果我地喺香港可以自發搞到啲活動一齊響應就更好啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;Support free expression for gamers everywhere we play!&rdquo;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mWo80nd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmWo80nd.jpg&h=7afc55ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8iOAFnf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8iOAFnf.jpg&h=00e754af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dswKyHk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdswKyHk.jpg&h=80dde1d0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b2970f160c7aae1700a3bec7543d121e6a797629","tid":1671305,"uid":54472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:39:32.000Z","msg":"開錯cc台冇人理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過希望大家可以多啲關注呢條戰線"},{"pid":"c4d91e02fa0d01f820371a949a6c5815816f605b","tid":1671305,"uid":54472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:42:25.000Z","msg":"pishhhhhh"},{"pid":"72caf0395f15e56e8aba75c918049c4c39fe2910","tid":1671305,"uid":54472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:43:54.000Z","msg":"pishhhh"}]}